Package com.jgalgo

package com.jgalgo
Parent package for all modules of the JGAlgo library.

Contains global configurations.

The package com.jgalgo.internal and its sub-packages are for internal use only. Please do not use them directly. They may be removed or changed without notice. Documentation is not generated for them.

    Graphs object are the fundamental building blocks of the JGAlgo library.
    com.jgalgo.io
